                  , in a certain passage in the King's highway, on the <rs id="t18220417-38-cd197" type="crimeDate">30th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-38-off196 t18220417-38-cd197"></join>, putting him in fear, and taking from his person, and against his will, one tin box, value 1 s., and one sovereign
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220417-38-victim407" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Newsam
